  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-4115" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://sassandveracity.com" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">kellypea</a></cite></div>
      <a href="index.html?p=1622#comment-4115"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2009-09-15T22:56:27-04:00">Tuesday, September 15, 2009 at 10:56 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>It&#39;s been forever since I had a lovely marinated chevre.  Both of your recipes sound wonderful.  Skipping dinner quality ; )</p>
    </div>

